data.description: A RARE PROPERTY! 14.65 Acres with all redone 4 bedroom, 2 bath home, that has an attached 40' x 30' garage.  the home has replacement windows, permanent siding, new kitchen and main floor laundry.  The property is set up perfectly for horses or other livestock with a good large barn, pasture, timber area and alfalfa field.  Additional buildings include another barn, wood corn crib, chicken coop and small machine shed.  There would be plenty of room to have a second homestead on this property.  Rural and well water to the property.
